mg_sohigh_course_v3

Killing course map. I didnt see any outdoor maps so i made new one.

Features:
- Random Light System:
   - "Night Lights" time
   - "Sunny Day" time
- City rooftops atmosphere
- Unique traps
- SpawnKill in 40 seconds
- 64 slots
- Grenades (trails)
- Grenades (secrets)
- First (main) challenge - 100 points
- Bonus challenge - 100 points
- Secret luck challenge - 100 points
- Music at all challenges
- Some custom textures
- NavFile

requires noblock
